{"tid":386591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖多字] 獨遊日本四國六日之旅 2","createTime":"2017-09-04T03:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T04:14:44.000Z","uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b27b043ad6bd0fbf2935c3f6e3d9fc5b7f8e81c","tid":386591,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:54:51.000Z","msg":"首先其實好多謝大家捧場<br />\n真係無諗過一個小小既遊記會有幾位巴絲打一直都傾下四國野<br />\n令到個post可以開到2<br />\n講真，如果幫到大家，我係非常高興，係達到我初衷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或許有部分巴絲打可能未睇過之前個遊記<br />\n下面條link就係<ins><strong>[多圖多字] 獨遊日本四國六日之旅</strong></ins><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/232912/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/232912/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不過為左方便大家，我都重新copy多次個遊記係呢度<br />\n等大家有咩想分享或者有疑問都可以直接係度睇完問<br />\n免得Click黎Click去<br />\n<br />\n而且其實有關日本中國地區、四國地區、關西同關東地區都可以問下<br />\n小弟都對呢幾個地域比較熟悉<br />\n<br />\n除左可以係lihkg收睇個遊記之外<br />\n其實小弟都係個別渠道post過遊記，所以大家如果係其他forum見到個遊記都唔洗驚係有人抄我<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.ulifestyle.com.hk/blogger/kky1216/page/5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fblogger%2Fkky1216%2Fpage%2F5%2F&d=yONfs0eKXJyP2eoWDhuRzozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=31fd157b\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.ulifestyle.com.hk/blogger/kky1216/page/5/</a> [老港孩Charles的生活點滴]<br />\n大家可以click上面條link，直接選取單元都一樣好方便<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果大家中意我個遊記、曾經比過正皮比&lt;獨遊日本四國六日之旅1&gt; 或者想支持下小弟既，都希望可以唔好吝嗇比個正皮我啦"},{"pid":"1b17643df1bcc1618cb62b1941a97b727395ab7d","tid":386591,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"首先好多謝大家支持我上一篇嘅一人東京遊記啦<br />\n想重溫可以click下面個網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/101577/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/101577/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n而今次呢篇遊記其實我之前都係東京遊記做過預告<br />\n我係30/4-5/5呢段期間會隻身前往四國<br />\n<br />\n係遊記開始之前，等我稍稍為大家介紹下日本四國呢個地方<br />\n四國位於關西嘅左邊，山陽嘅南方<br />\n四國係由四個縣--高知縣、香川縣、德島縣及愛媛縣組成<br />\n當地係屬於日本二線尾三線頭地區<br />\n物產唔算好豐富、交通唔算好發達、商業發展唔算好蓬勃<br />\n但正正如此，四國就保留左一種獨有嘅樸素感，令人身心舒暢<br />\n<br />\n而係香港要前往四國有以下幾個比較常見方法<br />\n1. HK Express直航去到香川縣高松市<br />\n2. 關西機場轉乘巴士前往四國各地區<br />\n3. 岡山機場轉乘巴士前往四國各地區<br />\n4. 岡山轉乘JR前往四國各地區<br />\n5. 廣島轉乘渡輪前往愛媛縣<br />\n6. 東京機場轉乘内陸機前往四國各地區<br />\n<br />\n而我就選擇左第一種方法，因爲最平！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講到旅行，除左關心行程之外，當然都好重視budget呢方面<br />\n我就先同大家分享下我呢個旅程洗費先啦<br />\n<br />\n機票：HKD431 (hk express megasale個陣買，不包行李)<br />\n酒店：約HKD1100 (5晚--2晚酒店+3晚airbnb)<br />\n觀光：約6700Yen (以7算則為HKD470)<br />\n交通：約15700Yen (以7算則約HKD1100)<br />\n飲食：約12000Yen (以7算則約HKD840)<br />\n其它雜項(Locker)：1000Yen (以7算則為HKD70)<br />\n屎忽痕洗費(零食、手信等不必要開支)：7050 Yen (以7算則約HKD490)<br />\n電話卡：HKD75<br />\n<br />\ntotal = 約HKD 4600<br />\n<br />\n只要你並非大洗之人，我認爲5-6日 HKD5000係絕對無問題<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n以下會為大家分享下我成個行程<br />\n<br />\n第一日：<br />\n(原先行程) 抵達高松--&gt;栗林公園--&gt;Check-in--&gt;鶴丸烏冬晚餐<br />\n但最後因爲HK express早左10分鐘到達而令我趕得切上一班出市區嘅巴士，最後行程改爲 <br />\n抵達高松--&gt; 金刀比羅宮 --&gt; Check-in --&gt; 鶴丸烏冬晚餐<br />\n<br />\n第二日：<br />\n前往四萬十川 --&gt; 高知Check-in --&gt; 播磨屋橋 --&gt; ひろめ(hirome)市場晚餐<br />\n<br />\n第三日：<br />\n前往大步危 --&gt; 祖谷蔓橋 --&gt; 大步危遊覽船 --&gt; 麵王晚餐<br />\n<br />\n第四日：<br />\n前往鳴門 --&gt; 鳴門觀光船睇漩渦 --&gt; 展望台睇鳴門大橋 --&gt; 渦之道 --&gt; 眉山 --&gt; 阿波舞會館 --&gt; 德島東大晚餐<br />\n<br />\n第五日：<br />\n前往高松 --&gt; 栗林公園 --&gt; 上原屋烏冬午餐 --&gt; 丸龜 --&gt; 一鶴晚餐 --&gt; 瓦町商店街<br />\n<br />\n第六日：<br />\n前往小豆島 --&gt; 橄欖公園 --&gt; 天使之路 --&gt; 返回高松 --&gt;前往機場<br />\n<br />\n由於只得六日時間，所以我放棄愛媛縣呢個比較遠嘅城市<br />\n而好似屋島、桂濱呢d其實我都好想去，但無奈地受時間所限<br />\n只能去左d我更想去嘅先<br />\n<br />\n我行程相對上次東京之行就輕鬆得多<br />\n原因係遷就每日都要好早起身 所以相對就早少少完成行程<br />\n更何況四國其實係無乜夜生活㗎<br />\n主要夜晚都係居酒屋爲主<br />\n過左8點條街人數寥寥可數<br />\n<br />\n遊覽四國有幾點要注意<br />\n1. 上述提及過左夜晚8點條街人數寥寥可數，而且夜晚都無乜夜生活。<br />\n<br />\n2. 高松相對係購物方面係最方便，因爲有幾個大型商店街及商場，更加有個開到比較夜嘅 Youme Town ; 而德島除左眉山、阿波舞之外，夜晚幾乎係0消遣活動；高知夜晚都仲係有少量超級市場可以行下<br />\n<br />\n3. 自駕遊人士定必小心，因爲四國駕駛人士我認爲係日本多個城市裏面比較唔讓人嘅一批<br />\n<br />\n4. 由於四國尚未係發展中地區，因此好多景點嘅交通配套都並不完善。有好多時搭完JR，都要係車站度等一段時間先有巴士轉載到其它景點<br />\n<br />\n5. 黎得四國就應該要有心理準備係真係睇風景爲主，唔好成日將購物掛係嘴邊"},{"pid":"aaee2489a3da553138b8a6fd9524eb832813bf44","tid":386591,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/fu/yX/fuyXHja98zZb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Ffu%2FyX%2FfuyXHja98zZb.jpg&h=4ba4bf1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係香港時間0850準時出發前往高松<br />\n<br />\n其實我呢一日係拖住十分疲倦嘅身軀出發<br />\n事緣出發前個一晚我打完3粒鐘波之外仲只係訓左2個鐘就出發<br />\n<br />\n我平時係搭車好難入睡嘅人<br />\n但我以爲今次應該無問題之際，上到機無耐就聼到有bb喊..WTF<br />\n<br />\n然後我全程就無訓過<br />\n<br />\n講返買四國鐵路周遊卷方面<br />\n其實UO上面係有得賣，而且價錢都十分唔錯<br />\n超建議大家係度買，除非klook/kkday做discount<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/nM/jv/nMjv89hWOrwM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FnM%2Fjv%2FnMjv89hWOrwM.jpg&h=7212d42d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我個人無係UO上面買<br />\n點解我咁豬？其實係我之前係Yen 6.6匯率個陣已經唱左些少<br />\n所以兌番hkd 我係當地買係平過我係飛機上面買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概3個鐘多d就已經抵達高松機場<br />\n<br />\n由於高松機場真係一個無乜航班又細嘅機場<br />\n加上我一個人無寄存行李<br />\n所以超快就正式進入日本境内<br />\n<br />\n我係先前都提及過班機係早左少少，而且入境手續非常快<br />\n所以我即刻走去買巴士卷 趕去高松站<br />\n好幸運地趕到巴士，所以將本來栗林公園改爲金刀比羅宮<br />\n<br />\n大家一出安檢就會見到買巴士卷嘅機器<br />\n先入錢 後禁你目的地就得<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/zr/tf/zrtfFaOFmAcb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fzr%2Ftf%2FzrtfFaOFmAcb.jpg&h=7fd0a920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴士都叫坐得好舒服<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/iy/8a/iy8a8CmRnJgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fiy%2F8a%2Fiy8a8CmRnJgH.jpg&h=e95762fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n補充返<br />\n大家可以係以下條link睇下高松機場出市區巴士班次時間<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kotoden.co.jp/publichtm/bus/limousine/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotoden.co.jp%2Fpublichtm%2Fbus%2Flimousine%2Findex.html&d=yONfs0eKXJyP2eoWDhuRzozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=66eba886\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.kotoden.co.jp/publichtm/bus/limousine/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出到市區<br />\n我第一件事係去買四國鐵路周遊卷<br />\n就算你係飛機、旅行社、網站買左，你仍然都要去JR辦事處換真正嘅Pass<br />\n<br />\n巴士一落車就會見到高松站<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/H0/L3/H0L3w1AtUE1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FH0%2FL3%2FH0L3w1AtUE1E.jpg&h=a55a4abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行入去就會見到JR綠色牌辦事處<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/bm/UV/bmUVFLosS3mU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fbm%2FUV%2FbmUVFLosS3mU.jpg&h=c40b7cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我無係呢度換，因爲當時辦事處入面超多人排曬隊<br />\n再向前行少少就會見到呢個Travel agency <br />\n其實呢度都可以買/換個pass㗎<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/od/sJ/odsJdfCKoTtv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fod%2FsJ%2FodsJdfCKoTtv.jpg&h=0605938e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以邊一邊少人就去邊度啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/xb/ur/xburwUy4AUkw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fxb%2Fur%2FxburwUy4AUkw.jpg&h=b4c45cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我順便換埋我之後5日會用得上嘅指定席座位<br />\n但其實換唔換都一樣 <br />\n因爲四國JR特急列車嘅自由席其實好多，係多過指定席<br />\n所以大家不必擔心<br />\n<br />\n換完Pass 我第一時間並非搭車，而係要醫肚！！<br />\n我7點幾係香港機場M記食完早餐去到高松2點半都無食過野<br />\n見仲有15分鐘我就行左入隔離7-11買野食物啦<br />\n<br />\n我諗大家都知道日本便利店簡直係天堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/uN/WP/uNWPqiiwgTn9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FuN%2FWP%2FuNWPqiiwgTn9.jpg&h=ed3be22c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最後買左水、飯糰同漢堡<br />\n<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/UC/mM/UCmMqkFivNSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FUC%2FmM%2FUCmMqkFivNSY.jpg&h=c3c198f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叮熱左嘅漢堡包真係超級好味！<br />\n反而入面有原隻玉子蛋嘅飯糰就比較失色，中間流心部分幾乎無曬"},{"pid":"0ad1ba3caad412008a15d86702154ef3f0e9ecb3","tid":386591,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:09:52.000Z","msg":"拎住pass嘅各位就要行個條由職員檢查嘅路<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/I7/92/I792D9ALfCdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FI7%2F92%2FI792D9ALfCdo.jpg&h=e7932056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就搵返你要搭嘅列車嘅月台<br />\n高松站係四國算係最大型車站，有8個月台<br />\n而且四國就算係快速或特急都有好多款列車<br />\n有新有舊，有d更加係以麵包超人為主題<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/tV/L0/tVL0c8GpaDCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FtV%2FL0%2FtVL0c8GpaDCF.jpg&h=895e24fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快我就已經抵達琴平站<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/yl/Ik/ylIkFVLyh448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fyl%2FIk%2FylIkFVLyh448.jpg&h=cd97c8e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車站有一種歐陸嘅感覺<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Oi/Tj/OiTj3inahGeF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FOi%2FTj%2FOiTj3inahGeF.jpg&h=55f4bb53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從JR琴平站行過去金刀比羅宮會經過琴平電鐵琴平站、大宮橋<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/F2/8U/F28U40F4ptgL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FF2%2F8U%2FF28U40F4ptgL.jpg&h=61516d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Uo/YI/UoYIgk8pobmB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FUo%2FYI%2FUoYIgk8pobmB.jpg&h=3749802c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/E4/Ju/E4JuqThCV5O1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FE4%2FJu%2FE4JuqThCV5O1.jpg&h=d8c8e6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/7V/Yc/7VYcVqxHqapE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F7V%2FYc%2F7VYcVqxHqapE.jpg&h=7199926e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概行10分鐘就會到達參道<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/4n/x6/4nx6nDTmCUfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F4n%2Fx6%2F4nx6nDTmCUfc.jpg&h=12620e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢間中野烏龍麵學校係教人手整烏龍麵(即係烏冬)<br />\n如果大家有興趣都可以去報名參加<br />\n<img src=\"https://myalbum.com/photo/rzKmEfP7WqeV_WkMm5g/1k0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyalbum.com%2Fphoto%2FrzKmEfP7WqeV_WkMm5g%2F1k0.jpg&h=0d069360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一日陽光普照<br />\n怕熱嘅我當然要搵雪糕消暑<br />\n我就搵左一間食蜜糖雪糕嘅鋪頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Yk/eA/YkeAvdDdjnUC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FYk%2FeA%2FYkeAvdDdjnUC.jpg&h=ea6cf506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後叫左杯柚子蜜雪糕<br />\nd柚子蜜超多 毫不吝嗇<br />\n唔係死甜個種 入口好舒服<br />\n而且雪糕係好綿好滑<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/gN/CY/gNCYzzM4piMY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FgN%2FCY%2FgNCYzzM4piMY.jpg&h=c478c952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我就正式向1368級樓梯進發！<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/XF/ZU/XFZUhMjn0aK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FXF%2FZU%2FXFZUhMjn0aK5.jpg&h=9732e7b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img][/img]<br />\n <br />\n起初以爲好少人<br />\n因爲一開頭個條路都無乜人<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/NV/qN/NVqNbWL7lkyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FNV%2FqN%2FNVqNbWL7lkyB.jpg&h=e3c6ccd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路都有唔少商店<br />\n有手信鋪同小食店<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/KZ/11/KZ11M2UQkapB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FKZ%2F11%2FKZ11M2UQkapB.jpg&h=34a06d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有d鋪頭都會提供免費竹竿比大家撐上去<br />\n但我一開頭無用 去到中途d鋪頭已經要比錢<br />\n大家記住寫住&rdquo;無料&rdquo;先好攞<br />\n<br />\n行左四分一左右就發現原來人都好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/yW/9T/yW9TTHYnfHcy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FyW%2F9T%2FyW9TTHYnfHcy.jpg&h=f53012d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實沿路環境都好清幽<br />\n而且佳木秀而繁蔭<br />\n令我行得都好舒服<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/QL/1n/QL1n7enL1Obh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FQL%2F1n%2FQL1n7enL1Obh.jpg&h=9430b7bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/sS/8F/sS8FkSlZpQG5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FsS%2F8F%2FsS8FkSlZpQG5.jpg&h=88c4c4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Jl/hP/JlhPgvI8pfHR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FJl%2FhP%2FJlhPgvI8pfHR.jpg&h=2db92b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Ue/zs/UezsIIdMOPMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FUe%2Fzs%2FUezsIIdMOPMr.jpg&h=47390ced&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度連馬都有得睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/lc/6F/lc6Fohr3iSXl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Flc%2F6F%2Flc6Fohr3iSXl.jpg&h=674d69e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然話每行一段樓梯就會有一小段平路<br />\n但樓梯源源不絕<br />\n好似行極都行唔曬<br />\n尤其好似我完全唔夠訓嘅人都有d辛苦<br />\n<br />\n好唔容易行上去旭社<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/jR/hm/jRhmXyBll1sQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FjR%2Fhm%2FjRhmXyBll1sQ.jpg&h=75392e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身想話係個度坐一陣<br />\n但望下地圖又好似爭少少就到本宮<br />\n所以都咬緊牙關行上去本宮<br />\n望見d樓梯就唔想行<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/EV/yZ/EVyZK9sj2LPu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FEV%2FyZ%2FEVyZK9sj2LPu.jpg&h=79b06f77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce4bfa4267d1eb63e3b69219a978dfa818a0480b","tid":386591,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:10:24.000Z","msg":"我好辛苦地趴左上本宮<br />\n我自己由參道行上本宮用左半個鐘頭<br />\n辛辛苦苦上到黎一定要周圍影下相<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/5Z/zU/5ZzUyW3w8kYt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F5Z%2FzU%2F5ZzUyW3w8kYt.jpg&h=7effb889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/kK/bC/kKbCdIhuhgTS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FkK%2FbC%2FkKbCdIhuhgTS.jpg&h=b14413fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉 如果我有錢可以買個廣角鏡就好<br />\n惟有用住部cheap cheap相機頂住檔先<br />\n<br />\n係本宮呢度望出去會望到好靚嘅景色<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/hk/eF/hkeFeFajRsQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fhk%2FeF%2FhkeFeFajRsQE.jpg&h=34eb25e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/uG/VL/uGVL7ie38RGa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FuG%2FVL%2FuGVL7ie38RGa.jpg&h=15b1283d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家不妨係度影下相 當作休息下<br />\n<br />\n而且係呢度有好多款御守賣<br />\n當中最特別係有呢一款金黃色御守<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/SN/Ni/SNNiTakAbv34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FSN%2FNi%2FSNNiTakAbv34.jpg&h=76ece306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但價錢&hellip;.都要800Yen<br />\n<br />\n當時天色開始變淡<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/NC/yu/NCyuaSXhcqCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FNC%2Fyu%2FNCyuaSXhcqCG.jpg&h=aa8c839f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最後並無上到去奧社<br />\n因爲我實在太攰<br />\n我應該一開始上山個陣行慢少少保存多d體力<br />\n由本宮行上奧社大概30分鐘左右就可以<br />\n但好可惜我最後選擇放棄<br />\n<br />\n如果你問我金刀比羅宮值唔值得黎<br />\n我會答你：被譽爲日本最難參拜寺廟，一試無妨，再試投降<br />\n呢個神社價值我個人認爲在於整個參拜過程<br />\n單論神社外觀設計其實普普通通<br />\n<br />\n補返多d相先<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/vF/3C/vF3Cn8zDL123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FvF%2F3C%2FvF3Cn8zDL123.jpg&h=f9c7f052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/0c/BQ/0cBQI7uJivMz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F0c%2FBQ%2F0cBQI7uJivMz.jpg&h=9e63c7ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/HY/nj/HYnjkcKwaphQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FHY%2Fnj%2FHYnjkcKwaphQ.jpg&h=3667d076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係臨近參道商店街有一間賣凍肉店<br />\n個度炸野聽聞都好受歡迎，大家不妨試下<br />\n唔好食唔好賴我啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/jr/pL/jrpLNd8HLMOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fjr%2FpL%2FjrpLNd8HLMOb.jpg&h=03fbee4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但實際上個商店街&hellip;.好冷清<br />\n<img src=\"https://myalbum.com/photo/ptfmOiqeNw67_ort6uJ/1k0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyalbum.com%2Fphoto%2FptfmOiqeNw67_ort6uJ%2F1k0.jpg&h=78fe549e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n安全地企係路軌上面打卡是常識吧<br />\n但記得一定要安全地進行<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/lU/kI/lUkIUNsIJLlK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FlU%2FkI%2FlUkIUNsIJLlK.jpg&h=e4217b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對面係麵包超人主題列車！<br />\n可惡 唔係我個班<br />\n(但之後幾日我都好榮幸地搭到 )<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/yD/Us/yDUsdh9VC8sJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FyD%2FUs%2FyDUsdh9VC8sJ.jpg&h=f852ad24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n我會形容我第一日高松係超級慘情<br />\n點解？等我講比大家聼<br />\n<br />\n返番高松站，我就準備轉另一架JR去栗林站<br />\n我今次選擇嘅酒店位於栗林站<br />\n叫做高松陽光商務酒店<br />\n原因有兩個<br />\n1. 乾淨企理<br />\n2. 好平<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/dt/sd/dtsdSLAzUaC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fdt%2Fsd%2FdtsdSLAzUaC1.jpg&h=ec869c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比大家望下内籠係點<br />\n麻雀雖小但五臟俱全<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/H4/bK/H4bK1F49Z5ZZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FH4%2FbK%2FH4bK1F49Z5ZZ.jpg&h=cb6e334f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等我安頓左一陣<br />\n我就發覺出現左問題<br />\n大家有無留意到整間房得一個斜孭袋<br />\n我個背囊呢！！？？<br />\n<br />\n個刻我先醒起我出發去琴平前將d貴重野同背囊寄存左係高松站coin locker度<br />\n所以我只好死死地氣番去<br />\n<br />\n8點之後嘅高松站附近都叫做有小貓三兩隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/ma/RC/maRCXp4ZwN27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fma%2FRC%2FmaRCXp4ZwN27.jpg&h=65234384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今晚plan左食一間係瓦町嘅手打烏冬店&ndash;鶴丸<br />\n鶴丸係淨做晚市同深宵生意，8點先開門<br />\n但我去度個陣先發現呢一日無開門 <br />\n<br />\n我個刻真係欲哭無淚<br />\n因爲視線範圍内都係一d居酒屋、貴價鋪頭同拉麵店<br />\n我plan左黎緊係德島都會食拉麵，所以唔想係高松都食拉麵<br />\n<br />\n我個刻係又飢餓又攰<br />\n根本連再搵餐廳嘅力都無<br />\n結果我走左入一間早餐/宵夜先會走入嘅地方&mdash;7-11<br />\n然後就攞左個我以前都試過嘅麻婆豆腐飯比錢叮熱<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/PW/FM/PWFMsQIi4T4l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FPW%2FFM%2FPWFMsQIi4T4l.jpg&h=4fd4a912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老實講句，其實個飯幾好食<br />\n而且真係有辣味，係有少少似四川<br />\n比起香港好多茶餐廳都正宗好多<br />\n<br />\n個刻我無感到任何失落<br />\n因爲突然有暖野填飽個肚已經覺得好辛苦<br />\n之後就係瓦町行返去酒店<br />\n<br />\n更加係酒店隔離超級市場買左盒士多啤梨做宵夜<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/it/E7/itE7LmbtTW7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fit%2FE7%2FitE7LmbtTW7r.jpg&h=487f3193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話瓦町站隔離有個藥妝店收10點<br />\n大家過左8點無節目不妨黎行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/GO/10/GO10JPc0h4AK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FGO%2F10%2FGO10JPc0h4AK.jpg&h=6d7fbd29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d05f7a2c7d6942349dc3d765c1b0f0ac9f24cf5","tid":386591,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T04:14:44.000Z","msg":"第二日 高知之行<br />\n<br />\n今日我6點半就起身<br />\n事關要趕7點幾嘅列車出發去高知！<br />\n而我今日目的地就係四萬十川<br />\n<br />\n我依舊係高松站7-11買我嘅早餐<br />\n個阿波尾雞飯糰真係超級好味啊！！！！！<br />\n入面醬汁濃厚，而且有微辣，好惹味<br />\n雞又夠嫩滑<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Fe/nJ/FenJ0i2Fygxz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FFe%2FnJ%2FFenJ0i2Fygxz.jpg&h=d9bbceee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次見到工作人員係其中一個站將兩架車組裝埋一齊<br />\n好得意<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/QB/Ky/QBKyesezKjPA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FQB%2FKy%2FQBKyesezKjPA.jpg&h=0be8c19c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路都係d鄉郊景色<br />\n好似返左大陸咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/3B/8r/3B8rU0umhTX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F3B%2F8r%2F3B8rU0umhTX4.jpg&h=65267a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/nE/pi/nEpiR9B2X5C8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FnE%2Fpi%2FnEpiR9B2X5C8.jpg&h=421e65dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n途中都經過大步危峽<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/YL/Zi/YLZiCgo2tbOB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FYL%2FZi%2FYLZiCgo2tbOB.jpg&h=5a16e85a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到高知<br />\n我第一時間係落去麵包店買第二次早餐<br />\n可能係生積 食極都唔飽<br />\n我買左呢個帽子麵包<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/r3/7R/r37Rpic7hgB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fr3%2F7R%2Fr37Rpic7hgB6.jpg&h=7345ddd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外層係蜂蜜蛋糕<br />\n而裏層就係普通麵包<br />\n有兩種口感，好特別，而且好正<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/q7/iI/q7iICyExvKLb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fq7%2FiI%2Fq7iICyExvKLb.jpg&h=d7d75860&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係高知站轉乘另一班開往中村站嘅列車<br />\n因爲要去四萬十川，較多人會選擇去中村站作爲出發點<br />\n<br />\n好開心今日有得坐麵包超人列車！<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Y1/o0/Y1o0wPT7cDw5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FY1%2Fo0%2FY1o0wPT7cDw5.jpg&h=4c09230d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概個半鐘頭車程<br />\n沿途景色怡人<br />\n有無敵大海景<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/fv/mf/fvmf1JD9TOwJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Ffv%2Fmf%2Ffvmf1JD9TOwJ.jpg&h=d9baf142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/bS/OB/bSOBqBCyxsv7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FbS%2FOB%2FbSOBqBCyxsv7.jpg&h=149cbe2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/LC/a4/LCa4fYBbnxhX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FLC%2Fa4%2FLCa4fYBbnxhX.jpg&h=fb6114bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/pj/rb/pjrbKR8GfBI5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fpj%2Frb%2FpjrbKR8GfBI5.jpg&h=3f5231ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過4個鐘車終於到達中村站<br />\n我個刻其實已經搭車搭到頭昏腦漲<br />\n<br />\n或者你地會問我點解唔上一晚落定高知<br />\n其實係高松去高知要2個鐘多d<br />\n如果我落機個日直接落高知就等同浪費一個下午<br />\n而且去到高知都唔早<br />\n我選擇上就去高知係我呢一日只會去四萬十川一個景點<br />\n所以時間會鬆動好多<br />\n<br />\n中村站休息室聽聞攞過獎<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/vE/Fw/vEFwoTOiHTGH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FvE%2FFw%2FvEFwoTOiHTGH.jpg&h=df1466a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我就出發去觀光案内所 (唔係無料案内所啊！)<br />\n首先中村站一出就向前行<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/PW/5g/PW5gWB7XuWdD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FPW%2F5g%2FPW5gWB7XuWdD.jpg&h=6c128bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後見到相中右邊路牌就左轉一直行<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/rY/Uv/rYUvdb6Pcee3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FrY%2FUv%2FrYUvdb6Pcee3.jpg&h=98bdfbf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一直行一直行你就會見到馬路斜對面有觀光案内所<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/zA/Y9/zAY9QDwmmq3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FzA%2FY9%2FzAY9QDwmmq3L.jpg&h=6909a8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行入去就會有人招呼你啦<br />\n會叫你選擇邊一款車<br />\n我自己就選擇左有得轉波嘅單車 價值1000Yen / 5hrs<br />\n而另外有d更加靚嘅電動單車就再貴500Yen以上<br />\n以前觀光案内所其實係有500Yen/5hrs嘅淑女單車<br />\n但而加無左sosad<br />\n<br />\n職員建議我5hrs可以踩去三里沉下橋<br />\n但我最後放棄<br />\n點解?<br />\n因爲我其實係出發前兩日先開始學識<br />\n我太虧 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我都唔敢亂踩太遠<br />\n萬一失誤就客死異鄉<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/2w/u1/2wu1c9MYMCPZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F2w%2Fu1%2F2wu1c9MYMCPZ.jpg&h=50a53c82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n租完單車就可以正式出發啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/vW/zt/vWztuvgoCbDl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FvW%2Fzt%2FvWztuvgoCbDl.jpg&h=63df3c4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路會經過一間便當店<br />\n我就刻意停車去買個便當<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/vg/oA/vgoAKeYYg9Lr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fvg%2FoA%2FvgoAKeYYg9Lr.jpg&h=d29c6b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n款式唔算多<br />\n而且以雞同炸野爲主<br />\n咁岩我去個陣d野食仲未擺曬出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/yl/cx/ylcxq181uaHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fyl%2Fcx%2Fylcxq181uaHy.jpg&h=0aea282e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而另外上圖左邊有d膠兜<br />\n自己選擇膠兜大細，價錢各異<br />\n之後你就可以任裝野食同白飯<br />\n好適合我呢d大胃王<br />\n<br />\n然後就正式出發"}]}